import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

temperatures = [95, 94, 83, 72, 71, 70, 69, 68, 67, 66, 65, 64, 63, 62, 61, 60, 59, 58, 57, 56, 55, 54, 53, 52]

# Plot the data as a line graph
